bio: Young Boy involved in Cryptocurrency and OPtimism Blockchain
impactDescription: Introduced OP to few of my friends, Got involved in Optimism airdrops like GRAIN and PIKA protocol. Hail Optimism as the best L2 on ethereum. Low gas fees and faster transactions.
